Figure 2:Overview ofSocialVeil.The pipeline consists of three stages:
(Barrier Injection) scenarios are neutralized to remove bias and barriers are systematically injected;
(Interaction Simulation) agents engage in multi-turn dialogue under barrier conditions;
(Evaluation) agent performance is assessed using automatic metrics (goal achievement, knowledge seeking, believability, relationship quality, confusion, mutual understanding) and human evaluation (alignment analysis and barrier navigation success).
